      "blocks": {
        "reason_rT3pY3": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "number": "",
            "title": "Hair Shedding Can Lag Behind Weight Loss",
            "body": "<p>Hair grows in cycles, so shedding may not appear when the trigger first occurs. Rapid weight loss can shift more follicles into their natural resting phase, with increased shedding becoming noticeable weeks or months later. It can feel alarming, but this type of shedding is often temporary.*</p>"
          }
        },
        "reason_bUpehB": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "number": "",
            "title": "A Smaller Appetite Can Mean a Smaller Nutrient Safety Net",
            "body": "<p>Eating less can also mean eating less variety, making it harder to consistently get nutrients associated with normal hair health, including biotin, zinc, and B vitamins. Bloomli helps supplement a balanced diet with those nutrients, plus marine collagen, in two daily gummies.*</p>"
          }
        },
        "r1": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "number": "",
            "title": "Biotin Is Only One Piece of the Hair Puzzle",
            "body": "<p>Biotin gets most of the attention, but healthy-looking hair relies on a broader nutritional foundation. Bloomli pairs biotin with zinc, vitamin C, B vitamins, silicon, PABA, and marine collagen, so your daily routine isn’t built around a single ingredient.*</p>"
          }
        },
        "r2": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "number": "",
            "title": "Hair Changes Take Patience, Not Bigger Promises",
            "body": "<p>Hair grows in cycles, so meaningful changes are measured in months, not days. Consistent nutritional support gives your hair time to move through its natural cycle without relying on unrealistic overnight promises.*</p>"
          }
        },
        "r3": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "number": "",
            "title": "A Routine Only Works If You Can Stick With It",
            "body": "<p>New medications and eating habits can make wellness feel complicated. Bloomli keeps hair support simple with two passion-fruit gummies a day. There are no large capsules, powders, mixing, or measuring.</p>"
          }
        },
        "r4": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "number": "",
            "title": "One Beauty Routine Can Offer More Than One Benefit",
            "body": "<p>Bloomli was created to support hair, skin, and nails from within. Its blend of biotin, zinc, vitamins C and E, and marine collagen makes it a simple addition to your broader beauty routine.*</p>"
          }
        },
        "r5": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "number": "",
            "title": "Quality Matters When You Take Something Every Day",
            "body": "<p>Bloomli is third-party tested for heavy metals, microbial contaminants, and label accuracy. It is made in the USA in an NSF-certified facility, because a daily supplement should earn your trust.*</p>"
          }
        }
      },
